Title: DJ Set: Boaconstructor
Book Description: 'Since 2011- Seattle-based 8-bit EDM producer boaconstructor has carved a name for himself pushing out huge bass tunes from a single Nintendo Gameboy.  Self-confessed to be disconnected from videogame culture- boa’s Gameboy use is aesthetic only- bringing less of the 80s- and more of the party. '
